fields.name: Cyber Security
fields.description: The Cyber Security Seminar, organized by the proactive Code Cell of RCoE, was an enlightening event aimed at deepening students' understanding of cyber security principles and practices. Held in the college lab, the seminar featured an engaging and informative session led by Fasal Bhati, a distinguished fourth-year Computer Science student with a keen interest and expertise in cyber security. Fasal Bhati captivated the audience with his comprehensive insights into various cyber security threats, defense mechanisms, and best practices to safeguard digital assets. His practical knowledge and hands-on experience provided attendees with valuable strategies to protect themselves and their organizations from cyber threats. The seminar also included an interactive Q&A session, where participants had the opportunity to discuss real-world cyber security challenges and solutions. This event not only enhanced the participants' knowledge but also inspired them to explore further studies and careers in the rapidly evolving field of cyber security. Organized by the innovative Code Cell RCoE, which is committed to fostering a culture of excellence and continuous learning in computer science, the Cyber Security Seminar was a significant step towards preparing students for the complexities of the digital age.

fields.name: Codeathon
fields.description: Codethon, hosted by the dynamic Code Cell of RCoE, is an exhilarating Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA) competition designed to challenge and hone the problem-solving skills of aspiring programmers. Conducted in the college lab, this event promises an intense coding experience that pushes participants to apply their theoretical knowledge to practical problems. Codethon features multiple rounds, each increasing in difficulty, covering basic to advanced DSA concepts, from array manipulation and string processing to complex graph algorithms and dynamic programming. Participants will be judged on the correctness, efficiency, and quality of their code. Attractive prizes, certificates, and exclusive opportunities for internships and mentorship programs await the top performers. Codethon not only offers a platform to sharpen DSA skills but also provides networking opportunities with peers and industry professionals. Organized by the innovative Code Cell RCoE, which is committed to fostering a culture of excellence and innovation in computer science, this competition is an excellent opportunity for participants to gain recognition, enhance their skills, and advance their careers in the tech industry. Register now and showcase your coding prowess in this exciting competition!
